nnovative writer for English readers.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aGerman poetryvTranslations into English. 0aGerman poetryx18th century. 0aGerman poetryxTranslations into English. 0aGerman poetryy18th century. 0aGerman poetry. 4aArea Studies : German Studies. 4aGeneral Interest : Poetry. 4aPhilosophy : Continental Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy : Philosophy. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Movements / General.2bisacsh1 aEzekiel, Anna C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143846199140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438461991423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438461991/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles